title: Let Go
message: You can’t control everything. Sometimes you just need to relax and have faith that things will work out. Let go a little and just let life happen.

title: Breathe
message: Worrying does not take away tomorrow’s troubles. It takes away today’s peace

title: Inner Strength
message: Anxiety happens when you think you have to figure out everything all at once. Breathe. You’re strong. You’ve got this. Take it day by day.

title: Trust the process
message: Turn your worry into worship and watch God turn your battles into blessings.

title: Perspective
message: Sometimes, all you need is a different perspective to see that things aren’t as bad as they seem.

title: Okay not to be okay
message: You don't have to control your thoughts. You just have to stop letting them control you

title: One day at a time
message: Take it one day at a time. Don’t stress yourself out about what’s to come.

title: In the Midst of Chaos
message: The greatest weapon against stress is our ability to choose one thought over another.

title: Embracing the Present
message: You can't always control what goes on outside, but you can always control what goes on inside.

title: Stillness in Motion
message: Sometimes you have to let go of the life you planned to make room for the life that is waiting for you.
